[The website had a confusing way of displaying list of flights. When I clicked on the desired flight, I did not actually 'select' it and the airline chose the first flight on the list by default. I ended up paying 11k for the wrong flight and now I am entitled to only 35&amp;#37; of the fare as refund. This literally happened in minutes. Why can't airlines issue a full refund accommodating for glitches like this. This is fucking diabolical!](https://preview.redd.it/vs1qo1od0cs81.png?width=538&amp;format=png&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=4aa8c006c51aecaebca136af02713bb723d80467)

